stylometry: Goal Seek is used when you are trying to get a particular result when your unsure of the starting value.  Data table is a tool that gives you the ability to see different results by altering the input cells of a function.  You can find these tools by going under the what if analysis key in excel.  An example would be trying to find the return rate such as in the catalog model we did to see the exact number of catalogs we should produce and changing the return rate which would vary the number of catalogs to be produced.
